    "title": "LazyStack .NET CLI Tool",
    "version": "3.0.1",
    "description": "LazyStack is a tool that ingests an OpenApi (swagger) REST API specification and generates the AWS Serverless \n    Application Model (SAM) template and the C# AWS Lambda projects necessary to stand up a fully featured \n    commercial-grade application stack in AWS. It also generates a client application SDK making it simple to \n    call that stack from C# applications."
